{"tid":2444862,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"歐錦棠網上分享亞視劇《精武門》片段 TVB投訴侵犯版權要求下架","createTime":"2021-03-13T07:05:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T20:30:37.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4680a2a3372d01e8893be42a176c491fe5fbb72d","tid":2444862,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T07:05:52.000Z","msg":"歐錦棠前日在其YouTube頻道《乜乜棠水舖》，以暢談形式分享1995年由亞洲電視拍攝的《精武門》幕後花絮，回顧他與甄子丹對打的場面。但上載不夠1天時間，歐錦棠隨即接獲TVB投訴，指《精武門》現有版權屬TVB所有，要求他立刻將有關該劇刪走或下架。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210313/IP7LGY7V5JH77BC3D5RW22ZX6Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210313%2FIP7LGY7V5JH77BC3D5RW22ZX6Q%2F&d=RYsttnILlo6fxd9QfZlXI3%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=41538280\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210313%2FIP7LGY7V5JH77BC3D5RW22ZX6Q%2F&h=f3a373d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210313/IP7LGY7V5JH77BC3D5RW22ZX6Q/</a>"},{"pid":"917dd7d6bf9b54f1f5c7548ffb1bb7f1b11f3d13","tid":2444862,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T09:25:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9d79c10776909fa0629c0d5a978422c0677ad155","tid":2444862,"uid":335924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T17:36:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48e8b752bd79fcfa336b1dadf88e4b72155a14e","tid":2444862,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T17:37:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8674017a8c7b2dde9be9a143d150238cc67bc21e","tid":2444862,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T17:38:04.000Z","msg":"放上odysee <img src